title: StarTalk Live: The Particle Party (Part 2)
description: The StarTalk Live “Particle Party” celebrating the discovery of the Higgs boson continues with Neil deGrasse Tyson, Bill Nye the Science Guy, CERN physicist Kyle Cranmer, comic co-host Eugene Mirman, Sarah Vowell and Scott Adsit.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
